title: $3500-3/2 Hollywood House-Privacy Fence-Garage-RAPID MOVE IN OK-Pet Ok
posting_body: ['Beautifully updated and freshly painted 3/2 single family home for rent.', 'Entire home is tile and wood floors, the living room and all bedrooms have brand new tile.', 'All windows have brand new blinds.', 'The home also has a garage with shelves, work spaces, and washer and dryer.', 'There is also an enclosed patio with brand new screening that leads to the massive fenced in back yard.', 'Also has an updated automated sprinkler system.', 'Minutes from I-95, Arts Park at Young Circle, downtown Hollywood, and the beach.', 'Home is on a well system, so no water bill.', 'This home is great for couples, families, pets, and get-togethers.', 'Can come partially furnished or not.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE – NOT SHORT TERM.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 2.5-3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
